'''Straw feminism''' is a [[straw man]] [[argument]] whereby exaggerated or fabricated elements of [[feminism]] are used in an attempt to refute and/or derail feminist arguments. A straw feminist then is a fabricated character used by those arguing against feminism to devalue and derail feminist arguments. Straw feminism often incorporates oversimplifications, misrepresentations and stereotypes of feminism in order to easily discredit feminism as a whole.<ref>{{Cite web|title = What is a Straw Feminist? (with pictures)|url = http://www.wisegeek.com/what-is-a-straw-feminist.htm|website = wiseGEEK|accessdate = 2015-11-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Feminist FrequencyTropes vs. Women: #6 The Straw Feminist "|url = http://feministfrequency.com/2011/09/23/tropes-vs-women-6-the-straw-feminist/|accessdate = 2015-11-06}}</ref>
